    sets the title of the <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000R.xml" title="Forests and trees of evergreen notes" addr="//forester/tfmt-000R" type="local">tree</fr:link>; can contain <fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-007O.xml" title="Forester markup: mainmatter" addr="//forester/jms-007O" type="local">mainmatter</fr:link> markup
  </html:td>
