    sets the <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000S.xml" title="Author of a tree" addr="//forester/tfmt-000S" type="local">author</fr:link> of the <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000R.xml" title="Forests and trees of evergreen notes" addr="//forester/tfmt-000R" type="local">tree</fr:link> to be the biographical tree at address <fr:code>name</fr:code>
