  <html:td xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">sets the taxon of the <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000R.xml" title="Forests and trees of evergreen notes" addr="//forester/tfmt-000R" type="local">tree</fr:link>; example taxa include <fr:code>lemma</fr:code>, <fr:code>theorem</fr:code>, <fr:code>person</fr:code>, <fr:code>reference</fr:code>; the latter two taxa are treated specially by <fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-005P.xml" title="Forester › release notes" addr="//forester/jms-005P" type="local">Forester</fr:link> for tracking biographical and bibliographical <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000R.xml" title="Forests and trees of evergreen notes" addr="//forester/tfmt-000R" type="local">trees</fr:link> respectively</html:td>
 </html:tr>

  
