                <fr:title text="Contributor to a tree">Contributor to a tree</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>A <fr:em>direct contributor</fr:em> to a <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000R.xml" title="Forests and trees of evergreen notes" addr="//forester/tfmt-000R" type="local">tree within a forest</fr:link> is either an <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000S.xml" title="Author of a tree" addr="//forester/tfmt-000S" type="local">author</fr:link> of the tree, or has contributed intellectually to the immediate content of the tree but cannot be held responsible for it.</fr:p>
                <fr:p>A <fr:em>contributor</fr:em> to a tree is someone who is a direct contributor to at least one tree lying within its <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000U.xml" title="The extent of a tree in a forest" addr="//forester/tfmt-000U" type="local">extent</fr:link>.</fr:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
